Valdosta.Sunset Hill Cemetery:
Sunset Hill Cemetery, located northwest of the intersection of North Oak Street and West Mary Street, is the oldest cemetery in Valdosta.


== Notable burials ==
These are some of the notable people interred in the cemetery:
Colonel William S. West, 1849‐1914. Builder of The Crescent (also listed as a National Historic Landmark in Lowndes County) and United States Senator.
